{
    "annotations": {
        "list": []
    },
    "description": "Workflow state timeline showing per-step status changes and time between transitions for each CR",
    "editable": true,
    "panels": [
        {
            "title": "Workflow State Timeline — assign-gpu-01",
            "description": "Shows what state each step is in over time. Green=completed, Yellow=waiting for external signal, Blue=running, Gray=pending",
            "type": "state-timeline",
            "gridPos": {
                "h": 10,
                "w": 24,
                "x": 0,
                "y": 0
            },
            "targets": [
                {
                    "expr": "compute_platform_step_status{cr=\"assign-gpu-01\"}",
                    "legendFormat": "{{step}}"
                }
            ],
            "fieldConfig": {
                "defaults": {
                    "custom": {
                        "fillOpacity": 80,
                        "lineWidth": 0
                    },
                    "mappings": [
                        {
                            "options": {
                                "0": {
                                    "text": "PENDING",
                                    "color": "#585858"
                                }
                            },
                            "type": "value"
                        },
                        {
                            "options": {
                                "1": {
                                    "text": "RUNNING",
                                    "color": "#3274D9"
                                }
                            },
                            "type": "value"
                        },
                        {
                            "options": {
                                "2": {
                                    "text": "COMPLETED",
                                    "color": "#73BF69"
                                }
                            },
                            "type": "value"
                        },
                        {
                            "options": {
                                "3": {
                                    "text": "WAITING",
                                    "color": "#FF9830"
                                }
                            },
                            "type": "value"
                        },
                        {
                            "options": {
                                "4": {
                                    "text": "FAILED",
                                    "color": "#F2495C"
                                }
                            },
                            "type": "value"
                        }
                    ],
                    "thresholds": {
                        "steps": [
                            {
                                "color": "#585858",
                                "value": null
                            },
                            {
                                "color": "#3274D9",
                                "value": 1
                            },
                            {
                                "color": "#73BF69",
                                "value": 2
                            },
                            {
                                "color": "#FF9830",
                                "value": 3
                            },
                            {
                                "color": "#F2495C",
                                "value": 4
                            }
                        ]
                    },
                    "color": {
                        "mode": "thresholds"
                    }
                }
            },
            "options": {
                "showValue": "always",
                "rowHeight": 0.85,
                "mergeValues": true,
                "alignValue": "center"
            }
        },
        {
            "title": "Step Duration (seconds)",
            "description": "Time taken for each step to complete. Longer bars = slower steps. Look for steps that take disproportionately long — they may indicate bottlenecks.",
            "type": "bargauge",
            "gridPos": {
                "h": 8,
                "w": 12,
                "x": 0,
                "y": 10
            },
            "targets": [
                {
                    "expr": "compute_platform_step_duration_seconds{cr=\"assign-gpu-01\"}",
                    "legendFormat": "{{step}}"
                }
            ],
            "fieldConfig": {
                "defaults": {
                    "unit": "s",
                    "thresholds": {
                        "steps": [
                            {
                                "color": "green",
                                "value": null
                            },
                            {
                                "color": "yellow",
                                "value": 5
                            },
                            {
                                "color": "red",
                                "value": 30
                            }
                        ]
                    },
                    "color": {
                        "mode": "thresholds"
                    }
                }
            },
            "options": {
                "orientation": "horizontal",
                "displayMode": "gradient",
                "showUnfilled": true,
                "valueMode": "text"
            }
        },
        {
            "title": "Current Workflow Step",
            "description": "Which step of the workflow is currently executing (1-5).",
            "type": "stat",
            "gridPos": {
                "h": 4,
                "w": 6,
                "x": 12,
                "y": 10
            },
            "targets": [
                {
                    "expr": "compute_platform_workflow_current_step",
                    "legendFormat": "Step"
                }
            ],
            "fieldConfig": {
                "defaults": {
                    "mappings": [
                        {
                            "options": {
                                "0": {
                                    "text": "Not Started"
                                }
                            },
                            "type": "value"
                        },
                        {
                            "options": {
                                "1": {
                                    "text": "① validate-spec"
                                }
                            },
                            "type": "value"
                        },
                        {
                            "options": {
                                "2": {
                                    "text": "② fetch-node"
                                }
                            },
                            "type": "value"
                        },
                        {
                            "options": {
                                "3": {
                                    "text": "③ set-owner-label"
                                }
                            },
                            "type": "value"
                        },
                        {
                            "options": {
                                "4": {
                                    "text": "④ wait-agent-ready"
                                }
                            },
                            "type": "value"
                        },
                        {
                            "options": {
                                "5": {
                                    "text": "⑤ update-configmap"
                                }
                            },
                            "type": "value"
                        }
                    ],
                    "thresholds": {
                        "steps": [
                            {
                                "color": "#585858",
                                "value": null
                            },
                            {
                                "color": "blue",
                                "value": 1
                            },
                            {
                                "color": "green",
                                "value": 5
                            }
                        ]
                    },
                    "color": {
                        "mode": "thresholds"
                    }
                }
            }
        },
        {
            "title": "CR Phase",
            "description": "Current CR phase: Pending → LabelApplied → AwaitingNodeAgent → Ready",
            "type": "stat",
            "gridPos": {
                "h": 4,
                "w": 6,
                "x": 18,
                "y": 10
            },
            "targets": [
                {
                    "expr": "compute_platform_cr_phase_total{phase=\"Ready\"} * 4 + compute_platform_cr_phase_total{phase=\"AwaitingNodeAgent\"} * 3 + compute_platform_cr_phase_total{phase=\"LabelApplied\"} * 2 + compute_platform_cr_phase_total{phase=\"Pending\"} * 1",
                    "legendFormat": "Phase"
                }
            ],
            "fieldConfig": {
                "defaults": {
                    "mappings": [
                        {
                            "options": {
                                "0": {
                                    "text": "Not Started"
                                }
                            },
                            "type": "value"
                        },
                        {
                            "options": {
                                "1": {
                                    "text": "Pending"
                                }
                            },
                            "type": "value"
                        },
                        {
                            "options": {
                                "2": {
                                    "text": "LabelApplied"
                                }
                            },
                            "type": "value"
                        },
                        {
                            "options": {
                                "3": {
                                    "text": "AwaitingNodeAgent"
                                }
                            },
                            "type": "value"
                        },
                        {
                            "options": {
                                "4": {
                                    "text": "✅ READY"
                                }
                            },
                            "type": "value"
                        }
                    ],
                    "thresholds": {
                        "steps": [
                            {
                                "color": "#585858",
                                "value": null
                            },
                            {
                                "color": "yellow",
                                "value": 1
                            },
                            {
                                "color": "blue",
                                "value": 2
                            },
                            {
                                "color": "orange",
                                "value": 3
                            },
                            {
                                "color": "green",
                                "value": 4
                            }
                        ]
                    },
                    "color": {
                        "mode": "thresholds"
                    }
                }
            }
        },
        {
            "title": "Reconciliations During Workflow",
            "description": "How many reconcile loops ran during the workflow execution. Requeues indicate the operator is polling for an external signal.",
            "type": "timeseries",
            "gridPos": {
                "h": 8,
                "w": 12,
                "x": 12,
                "y": 14
            },
            "targets": [
                {
                    "expr": "rate(controller_runtime_reconcile_total{controller=\"tenantnodeassignment\",result=\"success\"}[1m])",
                    "legendFormat": "success"
                },
                {
                    "expr": "rate(controller_runtime_reconcile_total{controller=\"tenantnodeassignment\",result=\"requeue\"}[1m])",
                    "legendFormat": "requeue (waiting)"
                }
            ],
            "fieldConfig": {
                "defaults": {
                    "unit": "ops",
                    "custom": {
                        "fillOpacity": 15
                    }
                },
                "overrides": [
                    {
                        "matcher": {
                            "id": "byName",
                            "options": "success"
                        },
                        "properties": [
                            {
                                "id": "color",
                                "value": {
                                    "fixedColor": "green",
                                    "mode": "fixed"
                                }
                            }
                        ]
                    },
                    {
                        "matcher": {
                            "id": "byName",
                            "options": "requeue (waiting)"
                        },
                        "properties": [
                            {
                                "id": "color",
                                "value": {
                                    "fixedColor": "orange",
                                    "mode": "fixed"
                                }
                            }
                        ]
                    }
                ]
            }
        },
        {
            "title": "Workflow Legend",
            "type": "text",
            "gridPos": {
                "h": 8,
                "w": 12,
                "x": 0,
                "y": 18
            },
            "options": {
                "mode": "markdown",
                "content": "## Node Assignment Workflow\n\n| # | Step | What Happens | Expected Duration |\n|---|------|-------------|-------------------|\n| ① | `validate-spec` | Check CR has owner + node | <1s |\n| ② | `fetch-node` | Get node from K8s API | <1s |\n| ③ | `set-owner-label` | Label node with owner | <2s |\n| ④ | `wait-agent-ready` | Poll for on-node agent ⏳ | 10-30s |\n| ⑤ | `update-configmap` | Record readiness | <1s |\n\n**Colors**: 🟢 Completed · 🟠 Waiting for signal · 🔵 Running · ⬜ Pending · 🔴 Failed"
            }
        }
    ],
    "schemaVersion": 39,
    "tags": [
        "operator",
        "workflow",
        "compute-platform"
    ],
    "time": {
        "from": "now-5m",
        "to": "now"
    },
    "title": "Compute Platform — Workflow State Timeline",
    "uid": "workflow-state-timeline",
    "version": 1
}